DEPENDENCIES
============
- atomic_ops library (e.g. libatomic_ops-devel-1.2-2.el5.x86_64.rpm)
- libconfig (www.hyperrealm.com/libconfig/)
- CxxTest

UNIT TESTING
============

1. Install CxxTest by anonymously checking it out via SVN (use empty password 
   when prompted).

   svn checkout http://cxxtest.tigris.org/svn/cxxtest/trunk cxxtest --username guest

2. Set CXXTEST_PATH in $MNEMOSYNE/configuration/default/test.py to point to the 
   directory where CxxTest is installed.

3. Type 'scons check' to build and run the unit tests.


Note: If unit tests do not build then you might need to add the following code 
at the end of $CXXTEST/python/cxxtest/cxxtestgen.py to make its main function 
callable.

   if __name__ == "__main__":
       main(sys.argv);
